messages.content:
你是 marketting-planning 项目的 attribute agent。
只围绕当前多轮营销规划链路归因：request_normalization、intent_recognition、field_clarification、session_merge、path_dispatch、planning_function、result_assembly、sse_generation、adapter_extraction。
优先定位最早造成 planning 输出不满足 reference contract 的阶段；如果 target_value_unit_probe、execution_stage_probe 或 planning_output_probe 已复现错误，必须以这些探针证据作为高优先级根因依据。
只能输出 AttributeResult JSON 所需字段；证据不足时用 evidence_strength=none/weak 和 root_cause_hypothesis 表达缺口。
最终只输出 AttributeResult JSON 所需字段：expectation_attributions、suspected_locations、root_cause_hypothesis、evidence、evidence_strength。

## 输出约束：attribute 归因分析输出
你的输出必须是合法 JSON，且严格符合以下 JSON Schema：
```json
{
  "type": "object",
  "properties": {
    "expectation_attributions": {
      "type": "array",
      "items": {
        "$ref": "#/$defs/ExpectationAttribution"
      },
      "minItems": 1
    },
    "suspected_locations": {
      "type": "array",
      "items": {}
    },
    "root_cause_hypothesis": {
      "type": "string",
      "minLength": 1
    },
    "evidence": {
      "type": "array",
      "items": {}
    },
    "evidence_strength": {
      "type": "string",
      "minLength": 1
    }
  },
  "additionalProperties": false,
  "$defs": {
    "ExpectationAttribution": {
      "type": "object",
      "properties": {
        "expectation_id": {
          "type": "string",
          "minLength": 1
        },
        "fulfillment_status": {
          "type": "string",
          "minLength": 1
        },
        "suspected_locations": {
          "type": "array",
          "items": {}
        },
        "root_cause_hypothesis": {
          "type": "string",
          "minLength": 1
        },
        "evidence": {
          "type": "array",
          "items": {}
        }
      },
      "additionalProperties": false,
      "required": [
        "expectation_id",
        "fulfillment_status"
      ]
    }
  },
  "required": [
    "expectation_attributions",
    "root_cause_hypothesis"
  ]
}
```

### 强约束
- 最终回答必须只包含一个 JSON object；不要输出 Markdown，不要使用 ```json 代码块，不要在 JSON 外输出解释、前缀或后缀。
- 最终回答首字符必须是 `{`，末字符必须是 `}`。
- JSON 字符串内部如需引用用户原词，禁止直接写未转义英文双引号；请使用中文引号“”或转义为 `\"`。
- 必须包含 `required` 列表中的所有字段。
- 每个字段值必须匹配 schema 中的类型。
- 以下字段必须非空（空字符串/空数组/空对象/None 均视为不合规，会被阻断）：['expectation_attributions', 'root_cause_hypothesis']
- `additionalProperties: false`：禁止输出 schema 未定义的字段。
- 禁止把 schema 里的类型描述符（如 "string"）原样当作内容填进去——每个字段必须填入真实内容。

{
  "expectation_attributions": [
    {
      "expectation_id": "意图分类正确且路由到营销规划相关阶段",
      "fulfillment_status": "not_fulfilled",
      "suspected_locations": [
        {
          "stage": "intent_recognition",
          "reason": "实际输出intent为4001（其他意图），stage为non_agent，与预期intent/clarification严重不符，导致整体链路偏离营销规划流程。"
        }
      ],
      "root_cause_hypothesis": "意图识别模块（intent_recognition）在接收到明确涉及NBEV、理财师、产品方案的营销规划类请求时，未能将其正确分类为营销规划意图，而是归类为“其他意图”，并错误地将阶段设为non_agent，使得后续field_clarification、planning_function等模块无法执行营销规划逻辑。可能原因包括意图分类模型覆盖缺失、特征提取不充分或阈值设定不当。",
      "evidence": [
        {"source": "extracted_output.turns[0]", "detail": "intent='4001', intent_name='其他意图', stage='non_agent'"},
        {"source": "execution_stage_probe.intent_recognition", "detail": "actual_stage='non_agent', expected_stage='intent'"},
        {"source": "planning_output_probe", "detail": "stage_match=false, actual_stage=null"},
        {"source": "reference_contract", "detail": "expected_stage='intent', scenario='intent_recognition'"}
      ]
    },
    {
      "expectation_id": "系统未触发 fallback",
      "fulfillment_status": "fulfilled",
      "suspected_locations": [],
      "root_cause_hypothesis": "系统在该场景下未使用fallback，符合预期，无归因问题。",
      "evidence": [
        {"source": "extracted_output.fallback", "detail": "used=false, allowed=false"}
      ]
    },
    {
      "expectation_id": "识别用户关注的业务指标 NBEV",
      "fulfillment_status": "not_fulfilled",
      "suspected_locations": [
        {
          "stage": "intent_recognition",
          "reason": "意图识别错误导致后续流程跳过，未对用户输入进行业务指标提取与确认。"
        }
      ],
      "root_cause_hypothesis": "由于intent_recognition阶段将请求误判为“其他意图”，系统未进入营销规划相关的指标分析与澄清流程，因此未能在输出中体现对NBEV指标的理解。根源仍为意图分类失败。",
      "evidence": [
        {"source": "extracted_output.robot_text", "detail": "仅包含“卡片生成完成”，无NBEV字样"},
        {"source": "extracted_output.card_summary", "detail": "为空数组，无任何指标信息"},
        {"source": "judge_result.fulfillment_assessments[2]", "detail": "期望未满足，score=0.0"}
      ]
    },
    {
      "expectation_id": "识别补缺拆解维度（增加理财师、优化产品）",
      "fulfillment_status": "not_fulfilled",
      "suspected_locations": [
        {
          "stage": "intent_recognition",
          "reason": "意图分类错误导致后续流程跳过，未对拆解维度进行识别或澄清。"
        }
      ],
      "root_cause_hypothesis": "同样因意图识别错误，系统未能进入规划拆解模块，输出中完全没有提及“理财师”或“产品方案”等拆解维度。",
      "evidence": [
        {"source": "extracted_output.robot_text", "detail": "无理财师/产品方案相关词汇"},
        {"source": "extracted_output.card_summary", "detail": "空数组"},
        {"source": "judge_result.fulfillment_assessments[3]", "detail": "期望未满足，score=0.0"}
      ]
    },
    {
      "expectation_id": "SSE 事件流包含营销规划相关事件",
      "fulfillment_status": "not_fulfilled",
      "suspected_locations": [
        {
          "stage": "intent_recognition",
          "reason": "意图错误导致planning_function未能生成有效卡片，尽管SSE流结构上包含planning_started等事件，但card_summary为空，属于无效流程。"
        },
        {
          "stage": "planning_function",
          "reason": "planning_function阶段返回card_count=0，未产出规划卡片。"
        }
      ],
      "root_cause_hypothesis": "意图识别错误使得planning_function接收到的上下文缺少有效的营销规划意图和所需字段，因此执行了空规划（card_count=0），导致虽然SSE事件流结构完整（包含了planning_started、card_delta等），但实质内容缺失，前端无法渲染有效信息。",
      "evidence": [
        {"source": "extracted_output.event_summary", "detail": "包含planning_started、card_delta事件"},
        {"source": "extracted_output.card_summary", "detail": "空数组，无有效卡片"},
        {"source": "planning_output_probe", "detail": "actual_cards_count=0"},
        {"source": "execution_trace.planning_function", "detail": "card_count=0"}
      ]
    }
  ],
  "suspected_locations": [
    {
      "stage": "intent_recognition",
      "status": "succeeded",
      "error": "输出intent=4001（其他意图），stage=non_agent，与预期营销规划意图严重不符，是造成所有下游期望失败的根因。"
    }
  ],
  "root_cause_hypothesis": "在intent_recognition阶段，负责意图分类的模型/逻辑未能将用户显式表达的“通过增加理财师或优化产品方案弥补NBEV缺口”识别为营销规划相关意图，反而错误归类为“其他意图”（4001），并将流程阶段设为non_agent。此单一错误导致field_clarification、planning_function等模块无法正确介入，造成后续所有业务指标识别、维度拆解和规划卡片生成期望全部落空。可能的原因包括意图模型训练未覆盖此类综合表达、分类阈值不合理或特征提取缺失。",
  "evidence": [
    {"source": "execution_stage_probe", "detail": "intent_recognition实际stage=non_agent，预期=intent；planning_output_probe显示actual_stage=null"},
    {"source": "extracted_output.turns[0]", "detail": "intent='4001', intent_name='其他意图'"},
    {"source": "judge_result.missing", "detail": "kind='intent', error_type='incorrect_intent'"},
    {"source": "reference_contract", "detail": "预期stage=intent, scenario=intent_recognition"}
  ],
  "evidence_strength": "high"
}

